mGLC changes list
---------------------

mGLC 0.3
- Added bitmap transformations (this means you can rotate text)
- Added support for font faces
- Fonts are now rendered correctly and in the correct position.

mGLC 0.2
- Non-functional, non-released version, supports basic bitmap rendering
  without GLX

mGLC 0.1
- Original version, supports basic bitmap rendering through GLX
